{"word":"Shewbread","slug":"shewbread","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Shewbread</b> General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=2'>Heb 9:2</a><br/> Called Hallowed Bread<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=6'>1Sa 21:6</a><br/> Ordinance concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=9'>Lev 24:9</a><br/> Required to be kept before the Lord continually<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=30'>Exo 25:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=4'>2Ch 2:4</a><br/> Provided by a yearly per capita tax<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=33'>Neh 10:33</a><br/> Prepared by the Levites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=32'>1Ch 9:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=29'>1Ch 23:29</a><br/> Unlawfully eaten by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=6'>1Sa 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=4'>Mat 12:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=2&verse=26'>Mar 2:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=4'>Luk 6:4</a><br/> Placed on the table of shewbread<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=23'>Exo 40:23</a><br/> Table of:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=2'>Heb 9:2</a> <br/> - Ordinances concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=28'>Exo 25:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=37&verse=15'>Exo 37:15</a> <br/> - Its situation in the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=35'>Exo 26:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=22'>Exo 40:22</a> <br/> - Furniture of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=30'>Exo 25:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=37&verse=16'>Exo 37:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=7'>Num 4:7</a> <br/> - Consecration of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=27'>Exo 30:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=29'>Exo 30:29</a> <br/> - How removed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=7'>Num 4:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=15'>Num 4:15</a> <br/> - For the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=48'>1Ki 7:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=50'>1Ki 7:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=19'>2Ch 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=22'>2Ch 4:22</a> "}]}